---
import Layout from "@/layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions | NodeFlux Pte. Ltd."
  description="Explore the terms and conditions for using NodeFlux Pte. Ltd.’s services, including the policies that govern your access to our website and digital solutions."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="space-y-12 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            Welcome to <span class="font-semibold">Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</span> (“Company”, “we”, “our”, “us”). We are committed to protecting your
            personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information
            when you use our services and website <a href="http://nodeflux.com" class="text-blue-500 underline">nodeflux.com</a> (the “Site”).
            If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at privacy@nodeflux.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Personal Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We collect personal data such as your name, email address, and phone number through forms where you provide consent to be
            contacted by us. We do not collect sensitive information such as financial data or government-issued identification numbers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Consent</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            By submitting your personal information through our forms, you consent to us contacting you for sales-related follow-up. You can
            withdraw your consent at any time by contacting us at privacy@nodeflux.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Purpose of Data Collection</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            The personal data we collect is used solely for contacting you regarding your interest in our services and for follow-up by our
            sales representatives.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We do not share your personal data with third parties. We also do not engage any external service providers for the processing
            or storage of your data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We retain the personal data collected for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by
            law. Our current data retention policy is to store data for a lifetime unless you request deletion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Data Protection Officer (DPO)</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            At this time, we do not have a Data Protection Officer (DPO) appointed. However, any data privacy concerns can be directed to
            privacy@nodeflux.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">8. Compliance with PDPA</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We comply with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA) of Singapore in the handling of all personal data. Your data is handled
            in a secure and lawful manner.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">9. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We do not use cookies or any other tracking mechanisms to collect personal information from users on our Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">10. Minors</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We do not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under the age of 18. If we become aware that we have
            inadvertently collected such information, we will take steps to delete it as soon as possible.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">11. Data Breach Protocol</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We currently do not have a formal data breach protocol. However, we are committed to safeguarding personal data and will inform
            affected individuals promptly should a breach occur.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">12. Changes to this Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. It is your responsibility to review this policy periodically to stay
            informed of any changes. We do not currently notify users of updates to this policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">13. International Operations</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            While we are currently based in Singapore, we are capable of offering services globally. However, the data we collect is
            governed by Singapore’s data protection laws.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">14. Data Deletion</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data at any time. To do so, please contact us at
            privacy@nodeflux.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">15. User Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            You have the right to access, update, or correct your personal data. You may also withdraw your consent to our processing of
            your data at any time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">16. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data handling practices, you can contact us via email at <a
              href="mailto:privacy@nodeflux.com"
              class="text-blue-500 underline">privacy@nodeflux.com</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
